{"arkId":"cl010099471","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099471","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre de forme \u0022tambour\u0022","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre de forme \u0022tambour\u0022"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Fran\u00e7ois II (1559-1560) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Valois-Angoul\u00eame) ; Charles IX (1560-1574) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Valois-Angoul\u00eame)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1550 - 1575","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1550,"endYear":1575,"imprecision":"","text":"3e quart du XVIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Schaufel, Veyt","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7018","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre de forme \u0022tambour\u0022, bo\u00eetier cylindrique grav\u00e9, comportant deux couvercles bord\u00e9s de moulures s\u0027ouvrant par deux charni\u00e8res fix\u00e9es sur la carrure au niveau du III. Sur le couvercle du mouvement apparait le Christ ressuscit\u00e9 b\u00e9nissant et tenant l\u0027oriflamme jointe \u00e0 la Croix, foulant un dragon. Couvercle oppos\u00e9 grav\u00e9, au centre de rinceaux et ajour\u00e9, sur son pourtour, de coeurs laissant voir les chiffres et les heures. Carrure orn\u00e9e de rinceaux fleuris grav\u00e9s en relief. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains et arabes (de 13 \u00e0 24), des petits points saillants permettent de conna\u00eetre l\u0027heure au toucher. Mouvement dot\u00e9 d\u0027un stackfreed, un foliot droit \u00e0 masselottes, \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre. Amplitude des oscillations du foliot pouvant \u00eatre r\u00e9gl\u00e9 par la pose de deux soies de porc.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; une t\u00eate de marotte ; un \u00e9cusson surmont\u00e9 du monogramme VS","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,3","displayDimension":"1,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"5","displayDimension":"5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : acier\r\nMat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Munich (Allemagne-\u003EBavi\u00e8re)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"19\/06\/1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Fran\u00e7ois II (1559-1560)"},{"value":"Charles IX (1560-1574)"}],"place":[{"value":"Munich"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliographyDate":"2000","bibliographyDetail":"n\u00b0 20","compariso